# USER-SERVICE Testing Document (Full QA Guide)

# 1. Service Information


Service Name : USER-SERVICE
Direct Port  : 8083
Gateway Port : 8081
Base Route   : /users/**
```

---

# 2. APIs Covered


GET    /users/me
PUT    /users/me
POST   /users/follow/{creatorId}
DELETE /users/follow/{creatorId}
GET    /users/following
```

---

# 3. Required Header

All APIs currently require:


X-User-Id
```

Example:

X-User-Id: 1
```

---

# 4. Test Environment


MySQL running
Eureka running
Gateway running
USER-SERVICE running
```

