# TEST CASE 2 — First Time Get My Profile

## Request


GET http://localhost:8083/users/me
X-User-Id: 1
```

## Expected Behavior

If user profile not present, service auto-creates.

## Expected Response


{
  "id": 1,
  "authUserId": 1,
  "displayName": "New User",
  "username": null,
  "bio": null,
  "avatarUrl": null,
  "country": null,
  "language": null
}
```

## DB Validation


select * from users_profile where auth_user_id = 1;
```

---

